pTitle: Lasko 754200 Ceramic Heater with Adjustable Thermostat
rText: Was looking for a heater for my office and this one is great. It is small enough to fit under my desk. You can either turn the heater on for when it is cold or you can turn the fan on when it gets hot. Awesome!

pDescr:

pTitle: Lasko 754200 Ceramic Heater with Adjustable Thermostat
rText: It heats up a small room and is perfect if you're just wanting to heat the bathroom before you shower. It does have a safety feature that I like and it's compact. But, it's not as economical as I thought it would be. And it doesn't do much for a larger room. If you get it for the purpose of heating a small room, you'll be very happy with it.
